OL,6,FOscar-winning actress hit out at
OL,7,Fgender pay disparity, saying she would
OL,8,Fget paid more if she was "Oliver
OL,9,FColman".
OL,11,FThe British star, known as the late
OL,12,FQueen in The Crown and for The
OL,13,FFavourite as the 18th century monarch
OL,14,FAnne, also dismissed suggestions that
OL,15,Fmale actors encourage cinemagoers to
OL,16,Fwatch movies.
OL,18,FColman was asked on CNN's Christiane
OL,19,FAmanpour programme about women being
OL,20,Ftaken more seriously in Hollywood.
