OL,6,FShe said: "Research suggests that
OL,7,Fthey've (women have) always been big
OL,8,Fbox office draws.
OL,10,F"Don't get me started on the pay
OL,11,Fdisparity but male actors get paid
OL,12,Fmore because they used to say they
